                }) %></p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Features -->
            <div class="features">
                <h3>‚ú® What You Can Do Now</h3>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="feature-icon">üõçÔ∏è</span>
                        Browse thousands of products across all categories
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="feature-icon">üõí</span>
