                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="feature-icon">üì¶</span>
                        Track your orders with real-time updates
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="feature-icon">‚≠ê</span>
                        Leave reviews and ratings for products you love
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="feature-icon">üéÅ</span>
